c: 3
v: 103
t: "And hold firmly to the rope of God and do not be divided. Remember God’s favour upon you when you were enemies, then He united your hearts, so you—by His grace—became brothers. And you were at the brink of a fiery pit and He saved you from it. This is how God makes His revelations clear to you, so that you may be ˹rightly˺ guided"